Second Department,

August, 1952.

(August 11, 1952.) Philip Wasserman et al., Appellants, v. Johnroy Properties, Inc., Tenant, and Rubymar Corporation, Respondent.

Motion for leave to appeal to the Appellate Division denied, without costs. Present — Nolan, P. J., Johnston, Wenzel and MaeCrate, JJ. [201 Mise. 744, revd. 202 Mise. 83.]
